gobblin.runtime.instance

Class StandardGobblinInstanceLauncher

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.google.common.util.concurrent.AbstractIdleService
      • gobblin.runtime.instance.StandardGobblinInstanceLauncher
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Service, Instrumentable, Configurable, GobblinInstanceEnvironment, GobblinInstanceLauncher

    public class StandardGobblinInstanceLauncher
extends AbstractIdleService
implements GobblinInstanceLauncher
    A standard implementation that expects the instance configuration to be passed from the outside. As a driver, it uses StandardGobblinInstanceDriver.
